decks.notes: The main concept of this deck is to aggressively overwhelm the opponent with a variety of low-cost creatures and spells, along with graveyard recursion and sacrifice effects to continuously pressure the opponent. Judith, the Scourge Diva, serves as the commander and provides additional damage whenever creatures die. The deck includes a mix of efficient creatures like Goblin Guide and Knight of the Ebon Legion, along with removal spells like Lightning Bolt and Fatal Push to control the board. Additionally, the deck utilizes cards like Reanimate and Demonic Tutor to bring back key threats or find specific answers when needed. The mana base is optimized to support the aggressive playstyle with a balanced mix of lands and color sources.
